  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
zdnet.com&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;high-speed-rail-20-trains-that-never-stophttpswwwzdnetcomarticlehigh-speed-rail-20-trains-that-never-stop&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.zdnet.com/article/high-speed-rail-20-trains-that-never-stop/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;High-speed rail 2.0: trains that never stop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Getting on a local train in Boston and getting off in San Francisco? A U.K. design firm says non-stop high-speed rail is the future of train travel.&lt;/p&gt;
